dct_alternative_sm: Engraved for Millar's New complete & universal system of geography
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, settlements, places of historical interest.
Features illustrated margins and illustrations of men in foreground.
From Millar's New complete & universal system of geography. London, A. Hogg, 1782.
